<H1>Today's Chemist at Work</h1>
<h2>December 1996</h2>
Today's Chemist at Work, <b>1996</b>, 5<i>(11)</i>, 52-54.
<h5><hr noshade>Copyright &#169; 1996 by the American Chemical Society.
<HR NOSHADE></h5>
<p><font color="red"><b>JAMES N. BeMILLER</b></font>   is a professor in
the Department of Food Science and director of the Center for
Carbohydrate Research at Purdue University. Formerly he was a faculty
member in the Departments of Chemistry and Medical Biochemistry. He has
written 200 journal articles and twenty-two books.</p><br>

