<HEAD>
<TITLE>TCAW 2/97 Author Information</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<H1>Today's Chemist at Work</h1>
<h2>February 1997</h2>
Today's Chemist at Work, <b>1997</b>, 6<i>(2)</i>, 112, 109.
<h5><hr noshade>Copyright &#169; 1997 by the American Chemical Society.
<hr noshade></h5>
<h3><font color="00008B">PATRICK P. MCCURDY</font>
is a consultant for
the American Chemical Society, editor of <i>Today's Chemist at
Work</i>, and former editor of <i>Chemical &
Engineering News</i> and <i>Chemical Week</i>.
<br><br>
<h3><a href="http://pubs.acs.org/hotartcl/tcaw/97/feb/prize.html">Return to
Article</a></h3>

</BODY>
