Today's Chemist at Work, <b>1996</b>, 5<i>(11)</i>, 48-50.
<h5><hr noshade>Copyright &#169; 1996 by the American Chemical Society.
<HR NOSHADE></h5>
<p>
<h3>Since 1987 <font color="maroon">Trevor
Smith</font> has been a medical and science
writer and is editor of <i>Running & FitNews</i>,
newsletter of the American Running & Fitness
Association, and a senior writer for <i>Men's Workout</i>
and <i>Exercise and Health</i>
magazines. He was formerly a group leader in the
physiology department of the Gillette Research Institute. He holds an
M.Sc. degree in chemistry from the University of London.</h3>
</p>
