<P>
<H3>
<IMG WIDTH="259" HEIGHT="24" SRC="join.gif"
ALT="Join The Ireland Funds">
<P>
Join the members of the Ireland Fund! For a discounted Internet membership rate of $25 you will receive:

<UL>
<LI> Connections - the in-depth magazine of the Ireland Funds
<LI> An e-mailed monthly update on Ireland Fund activities
<LI> A special Christmas gift - our thank you to you for your interest and involvement with the Ireland Funds.
</UL>
For more details on how you can become a member of The Ireland Funds please go <A HREF="../member/member.htm">here</A><BR>

<P>
