<HR SIZE="4">

<P> 
<B>
<H3>

 <FONT SIZE=+2>The Ireland Funds</FONT> are a confederation of concern linking
people from around the world with Ireland, North and South. With over 50 fundraising
events held annually in 40 cities around the world, the Funds have translated
Irish interest and ancestry into over $80 million of support for projects of
Peace, Culture and Charity in Ireland. </CENTER>

</H3> <P> <CENTER> <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Boston</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Dallas</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm#denver">Denver</A>
- <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Detroit</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Houston</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Phoenix</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Hartford</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Newport</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Chicago</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">New York</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Cape Cod</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Pittsburgh</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">San Diego</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Nantucket</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Los Angeles</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">Palm Beach</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Philadelphia</A> - <A
HREF="america/usa.htm">San Francisco</A> - <A HREF="america/usa.htm">Washington, DC</A>
* <A HREF="europe/ire.htm">Dublin</A> * <A HREF="europe/gb.htm">London</A> - <A
HREF="europe/gb.htm">Manchester</A> * <A HREF="europe/fr.htm">Paris</A> * <A
HREF="america/can.htm">Ottawa</A> - <A HREF="america/can.htm">Toronto</A> - <A
