<HEAD><TITLE>The Ireland Funds</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../gfx/pattern.gif" link="#0000ff"
vlink="#ff0000">


<IMG WIDTH="208" HEIGHT="29" SRC="../gfx/tif.gif" ALIGN="LEFT">
<A HREF="../welcome.html><IMG WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="61" SRC="../gfx/logo4.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" BORDER="0"></A>

<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<A HREF="projects.htm"><IMG WIDTH="51" HEIGHT="41"
SRC="../gfx/hibk4.gif" ALT="Back" BORDER="0" ALIGN="LEFT"></A><IMG
WIDTH="51" HEIGHT="41" SRC="../gfx/higryfw4.gif" ALT="Can't go
forward" BORDER="0" ALIGN="LEFT">
<BR CLEAR=ALL>



<CENTER><IMG WIDTH="532" HEIGHT="8" SRC="../gfx/lnbreak2.gif"
ALT="____________________"><BR>

<IMG WIDTH="430" HEIGHT="70" SRC="oak-bar.gif">
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE="4">
<B>
<H3>
<P>



<IMG WIDTH="140" HEIGHT="34" SRC="its_spring.gif" ALT=It's_Spring!> 
<BR>
<IMG WIDTH="89" HEIGHT="192" SRC="trees.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT>
In honor of the start of the season The Ireland Funds are now making it 
possible for you to plant a tree in Oak Glen, Co. Wicklow, Ireland. For several years,
 the Ireland Funds have been helping people around the world memorialize and 
 celebrate the lives of friends, family and special occasions while aiding in the 
 reforestation of Ireland. In conjunction with Crann - a non-profit organization in 
 County Wicklow, and Coillte - the Irish Forestry Board - we are now offering this 
 opportunity to our friends on the Internet.
<P>
 75% of Ireland used to be covered in Oak trees, today..only 1%. But you can help 
 bring the Irish Oak back to Ireland for the children of today and future generations.
<P>
For $25 a hand calligraphied scroll will be sent to you, or to the person you 
designate, and an Irish Oak tree will be planted in their name (or yours!). This is a 
wonderful gift to your friends and family and to Ireland.
<P>
Simply fill in the details below and e-mail with your credit card information, or 
print out this page and mail to the address in the order form.
<P>


<IMG WIDTH="219" HEIGHT="89" SRC="trees2.gif">
<CENTER>
<HR SIZE=4 WIDTH=80%>

<H2>Order Form</H2>
</CENTER>

Order as many trees as you like by clearing the form and submitting another request.
A personalized scroll will be sent to you or the person you designate, along with 
an acknowledgement of your gift.
<P>
Each individual tree is $25. Checks can be made out to The American Ireland Fund and 
mailed to 211 Congress Street, Boston MA 02110 - USA.


