<H2>Book of Kells</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<HR SIZE="4">
<B>
<H3>
<P>
<IMG WIDTH="216" HEIGHT="294" SRC="kells.gif" ALIGN="LEFT" HSPACE="10">
<FONT SIZE=+3>T</FONT>he Book of Kells is one of the great early Christian
manuscripts
proudly displayed in a new gallery in the Library of Dublin University (Trinity
College). With the help of The Ireland Funds a new exhibition and display center
provide
background relating to the book's creation and the monastic world of Ireland in
the
early Middle Ages.
