<H2>Shankill Community Information Service</H2>
</CENTER>  <P>
<HR SIZE="4">
<B>
<H3>
<P>
<IMG WIDTH="269" HEIGHT="213" SRC="shankill.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" HSPACE="10">
<FONT SIZE=+3>T</FONT>he Shankill People, a community newspaper published by the
Shankill
Community Information Services, confronts sectarian thinking and action and
encourages
positive dialogue in troubled North and West Belfast.
