<H2>Women's Information Drop-In Centre</H2>
</CENTER> 
<P>
<HR SIZE="4">
<B>
<H3>
<P>
<IMG WIDTH="181" HEIGHT="288" SRC="widic.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" HSPACE="10">
<FONT SIZE=+3>T</FONT>he courage of Joyce McCartan stands behind Belfast's
Women's
Information Drop-In Centre. Mrs McCartan, who lost three sons to sectarian
violence,
