<HEAD><TITLE>The Ireland Funds</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../gfx/pattern.gif" link="#0000ff"
vlink="#ff0000">

<A NAME="top1"> </A>
<A HREF="../welcome.html"><IMG WIDTH="70" HEIGHT="61" SRC="../gfx/logo4.gif" ALIGN="RIGHT" BORDER="0"></A>

<A HREF="projects.htm"><IMG WIDTH="51" HEIGHT="41" SRC="../gfx/hibk4.gif" ALT="Back" BORDER="0" ALIGN="MIDDLE"></A><IMG WIDTH="51" HEIGHT="41" SRC="../gfx/higryfw4.gif" ALT="Can't go forward" BORDER="0" ALIGN="MIDDLE"><BR>



<H2>The Ireland Funds Grants</H2>

<CENTER><IMG WIDTH="532" HEIGHT="8" SRC="../gfx/lnbreak2.gif" ALT="____________________"></CENTER><BR> 
<P>
<B>
In the last six years, The Ireland Funds have made grants of more than $23 million to more than 1,000 projects throughout Ireland, North and South. The following list describes a selection of the projects that have been grant aided. All grants are approved by the Irish Advisory Committee headed in Ireland by Dr. Maurice Hayes.
<P>

<HR SIZE="4">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2>
<A HREF="#a">A</A> -
<A HREF="#b">B</A> -
<A HREF="#c">C</A> -
<A HREF="#d">D</A> -
<A HREF="#e">E</A> -
<A HREF="#f">F</A> -
<A HREF="#g">G</A> -
<A HREF="#h">H</A> -
<A HREF="#i">I</A> -
<A HREF="#k">K</A> -
<A HREF="#l">L</A> -
<A HREF="#m">M</A> -
<A HREF="#n">N</A> -
<A HREF="#o">O</A> -
<A HREF="#p">P</A> -
<A HREF="#r">R</A> -
<A HREF="#s">S</A> -
<A HREF="#t">T</A> -
<A HREF="#u">U</A> -
<A HREF="#w">W</A> -
<A HREF="#y">Y</A>
</FONT></CENTER>
<HR SIZE="4">

<P>

<A NAME="a"><FONT SIZE=+3>A</FONT></A>idswise: Dublin, $12,200. To develop educational-resource material<BR><IMG WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="1" SRC="../gfx/space.gif">to heighten awareness and understanding of the HIV infection.<BR>
Alert: Dublin, $13,100. A national project formed to make young people <BR><IMG WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="1" SRC="../gfx/space.gif">more aware of the dangers involved in drug and alcohol abuse.<BR>

Alternative Entertainment: Dublin, $20,700. A community based arts <BR><IMG WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="1" SRC="../gfx/space.gif">group in Tallaght that tackles the problems of this area through <BR><IMG WIDTH="40" HEIGHT="1" SRC="../gfx/space.gif">workshops, creative writing classes, jazz, and traditional music.<BR>

