<P>


<H3>WATERSIDE COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT TRUST</H3>

Waterside Development Trust's efforts to promote economic development is part of
the effort to secure a promising future for all Derry residents. This is a three
year Pilot Scheme established to encourage and develop
self-help, and a cordial and co-operative society where Catholics and Protestants
can live together. The development plan includes jobs creation, training
programs, cross-community work and general community development.
<P>
<HR SIZE=2 WIDTH=40%>
<A HREF="graphics/p12b.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63"
SRC="graphics/p12b-sml.gif"
BORDER=0 ALIGN=CENTER></A>
Waterside Trust, Greenhouse Project, Derry
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=70%>

<H3>WEST BELFAST FESTIVAL</H3>
<IMG WIDTH="266" HEIGHT="300" SRC="graphics/p12a.gif" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
This innovative program seeks to raise cultural awareness and to provide
performance and artistic activity in West Belfast, an area characterized by
social deprivation and over the years by high levels of conflict. The Festival
has been highly successful and offers a varied and stimulating program. It has
spawned a number of continuing cultural activities and has created an audience
for artistic events in the area. It was among the groups endorsed by President
Robinson on her visit to West Belfast.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=70%>

<H3>SHANKILL TEAM MINISTRY</H3>

This is a key center of social interaction on the Shankill Road. It is a place
where cross-community contact can be made for all members of the community.
Services provided there by staff and volunteers include senior citizens
recreation groups, mother and toddler groups, day care center, advice and
counselling services and job training programs. In addition, the project also
contributes to many other developments which are assisting in the regeneration of
the Shankill.
<P>
<HR SIZE=2 WIDTH=40%>
<A HREF="graphics/p12c.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63"
SRC="graphics/p12c-sml.gif"
BORDER=0 ALIGN=CENTER></A>

Shankill Team Ministry, Child Day Care Center.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<A HREF="graphics/p12d.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63"
SRC="graphics/p12d-sml.gif"
BORDER=0 ALIGN=CENTER></A>

Shankill Team Ministry, Senior Citizens Group.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>





<P>

