<H2>1996 Donors</H2>

The American Ireland Fund would be nothing if it were not for the generosity of thousands of people. On these pages, we list the vast majority of our contributors for the first 5 months of this year. If we were to list all of our contributors over the last 20 years, from around the world, it would fill this magazine. On behalf of the thousands of Irish people whose lives have been made better through your generosity -
A Sincere Thank You.
