BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="ABSMIDDLE"></A> Mary Lou Whitney (center) with Joe and Eileen Cornacchio.

<P>
<A HREF="graphics/p22d.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63" SRC="graphics/p22d-sml.gif"
BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="LEFT"></A> The Dinner Committee: Mike Gibbons, Cynthia 
