<H2>Beantown Bash in Boston
<P>
The Angels of L.A.</H2>

Young Events with an Eye to the Future
<IMG WIDTH="255" HEIGHT="183" SRC="graphics/p26c.gif" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">

The American Ireland Fund enourages the next generation of supporters to take an 
interest in the work of the Fund both with stand alone events and by encouraging 
attendance at the major events. Already this year both Boston and Los Angeles have 
had "Young" events which attracted major support.

<BR CLEAR=RIGHT>

<P>
