<H2>Riverdance</H2>

<IMG WIDTH="247" HEIGHT="195" SRC="graphics/p27c.gif" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">

By now few people have not heard of Riverdance and the sensational impact this Irish 
music and dance extravaganza has had after a brief season at Radio City in New York. 
The American Ireland Fund was in attendance to pay tribute to a remarkable show.

