<A HREF="graphics/p28d.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63" SRC="graphics/p28d-sml.gif"
BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="LEFT"></A> Joe Bogdanovich passing on some seafaring tips to the captain of the Dun Laoghaire Lifeboat.
