<H2>Flying High in Phoenix</H2>
<IMG WIDTH="155" HEIGHT="275" SRC="graphics/p29a.gif" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="RIGHT">


In this, only the second year of the Phoenix Dinner, this event has now become firmly 
entrenched in the Phoenix social calendar. Co-Chaired by Jim Cunningham and Frank 
Leavy the dinner attracted nearly 400 people who were treated to a marvelous 
evening's entertainment. The Phoenix chapter honored Irish-American Dr. Stephen 
Flynn, for his humanitarian work in Mexico and also the incomparable Donald O'Connor 
who thrilled the audience by singing a few numbers from the past.
<BR CLEAR=RIGHT>
<P>
<A HREF="graphics/p29b.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63" SRC="graphics/p29b-sml.gif"
