<H2>Hats Off To Houston</H2>

The stars were out in houston to honor Lloyd Bentsen on April 25th. Under the 
chairmanship of Dan Breen, the second Houston Dinner was another resounding success. 
Dan and Pat Breen attracted a great gathering to the Houstonian Hotel to honor 
Secretary of State Lloyd Bentsen. A capacity crowd was treated to a vintage Bentsen 
address and was entertained by the talented Cactus Prior from Austin.

