BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="LEFT"></A><BR> Irish Ambassador to France Patrick 
O'Connor and his wife Patricia.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<A HREF="graphics/p32d.gif"><IMG WIDTH="78" HEIGHT="63" SRC="graphics/p32d-sml.gif"
BORDER="0" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="LEFT"></A><BR> Host of the evening, Philippe, Duke of 
Magenta, holding the Wild Geese Award.
<BR CLEAR=LEFT>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
For more information about The Ireland Fund of France, contact<BR>
Tadhg O'Sullivan, Vice Chairman,
The Ireland Fund of France, 2 Saint Thomas's Road, Mount Merrion, Co. Dublin, Ireland
Tel: (01) 283-3045:<BR>
Fax: (01) 283-5491

</B>
