<H2>The Ireland Funds' Newest Member</H2>

<IMG WIDTH="132" HEIGHT="186" SRC="graphics/p36.gif" HSPACE="10" ALIGN="LEFT">

the Ireland Funds are pleased to announce the appointment of Kieran McLoughlin as 
Director-Ireland with responsibility for running the Irish end of operations. A 
native of Dublin and graduate of Trinity College Dublin, Kieran has previously worked 
for the Dublin Chamber of Commerce and with the Dublin International Sports Council.

