<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Mountain Bike Pages</TITLE>
<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:Lindsay.Marshall@newcastle.ac.uk">
</HEAD><BODY BACKGROUND="/Images/Bg/shockbg2.gif">
<P ALIGN="CENTER">
<IMG SRC="/Images/Misc/mtbpages.gif" ALT="The Mountain Bike Pages"
WIDTH="540" HEIGHT="60"><BR>
</P><P>
This was a set of pages dedicated to Mountain Bikes and
things Mountain Biking with a particular emphasis on the UK.
</P>
<p>As you will I have noticed I haven't had the chance to update this
stuff for ages and the chances are receding even further so I have,
regretfully, decided to pull them for the moment. There are loads of
pages out there done by people who have the time to devote to scouring
the web for mtb related material. When I started these pages there
just wasn't that much stuff around.</P><P>
Thanks to everyone who has contributed items to me and sent me nice
e-mail. Yah, boo sucks to the people who sent me nasty e-mail...
</P>
<P>L.</P>
