<H2 ALIGN="CENTER">Lindsay Marshall's Home Page</H2>
</TD>
<TD ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="/edgefade.gif" WIDTH="160" HEIGHT="120" ALIGN="MIDDLE"
ALT="A picture of me...">
</TD>
</TABLE>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>Taste Warning:</B> This page is fairly
<A HREF="http://www.webpagesthatsuck.com/">crap</A> at the moment.</P>
<P>Welcome to <A HREF="/Lindsay.html">my home page</A>. 
I am a lecturer in the <A HREF="http://www.cs.ncl.ac.uk/">Department of
Computing Science</A> at the
<A HREF="http://www.ncl.ac.uk/">University of Newcastle upon Tyne</A>
where I teach courses in
<A  HREF="/csc201">programming</A> and software design. My
main research interests are Mobile computing, System Management,
Software Design and Distributed Computer Systems.
Currently my favourite programming system is
<A HREF="/Tcl-Tk_docs">tcl/tk</A>.
You can fetch some of my tcl/tk programs by
<A HREF="ftp://catless.ncl.ac.uk/pub">ftp</A> or
via the <A HREF="/Programs">web</A>.
I am also responsible for
<A HREF="/Admissions/undergrad.html">Undergraduate Admissions</A> to the
<A HREF="http://www.cs.ncl.ac.uk/">Department</A>.
If you want, you can find out
<A HREF="/Lindsay/interests.html">what interests me</A> or check out
<A HREF="/Lindsay/Links.html">my collection of links</A>.</P>
<P>The machine this is being sent to you from is
<A HREF="/welcome.html">catless.ncl.ac.uk</A> which is one of the machines that
sit on my <A HREF="/Lindsay/coords.html">desk</A>. Follow the link if
you want to know what <A HREF="/welcome.html">catless</A> means.
</P>
<P>On the web, I run <A HREF="/Obituary/README.html">The Obituary Pages</A>,
the <A HREF="/vmg">Virtual Memorial Garden</A>,
and the html version of the <A HREF="/Risks">Risks Digest</A>.
<A HREF="/welcome.html">Catless</A> also
hosts <A HREF="http://www.veg.org/veg">the Vegetarian Pages</A>, because I am one,
which is useful to know should you ever
<A HREF="mailto:Lindsay.Marshall@newcastle.ac.uk">invite</A> me round
for tea.</P>
