<A HREF="http://www.cs.ucl/misc/uk/intro.html">UK</A>NE1 7RU
</ADDRESS>
<P>
<IMG SRC="/Images/phone.gif" ALIGN="MIDDLE" ALT="Phone" WIDTH="32" HEIGHT="32">+44-191-222-8267
