</BLOCKQUOTE>
or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:Lindsay.Marshall@newcastle.ac.uk">Lindsay.Marshall@newcastle.ac.uk</A>.
<P>
A list of companies willing to offer sponsorship is published annually by:
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<ADDRESS>
