<A HREF="http://glimpse.cs.arizona.edu:1994/">glimpse</A> search engine.
An HTML version of the glimpse manual pages is
<A HREF="http://glimpse.cs.arizona.edu:1994/glimpsehelp.html">here.</A></P>
<P><B>Searching is slow - don't be impatient. Catless is not a very
powerful machine. You want fast searching? Get someone to donate me a
faster machine!!</B></P>

<FORM ACTION="http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/bin/riskssearch">
