</UL><DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT=p"o" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14">
<A HREF="/Risks/3.91.html">Volume 3 Issue 91 (30 Oct 86)</A>
<DD><UL>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/3.91.html#subj1">  Evolution, Progress (Jim Horning)</A>
