<A HREF="/Risks/5.20.html">Volume 5 Issue 20 (30 Jul 87)</A>
<DD><UL>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/5.20.html#subj1">  Lack of sanity at the IRS (Victor S. Miller)</A>
